pullRequest.title: pscanrule Release: ScanRule Consistency
pullRequest.bodyText:
Tweak

Scan Rule class names.
Scan Rule unittest names.
Message.properties keys (and some values).
Help content.
Remove a few unnecessary constructors.

PS > Yes I know this will end-up conflicting with the other CSP PR. I'll address the conflict after the other is merged.
Part of: zaproxy/zaproxy#6049
Signed-off-by: kingthorin kingthorin@users.noreply.github.com

nodes.bodyText:

Will tackle that in a bit and restore the relevant bits.
